# Autopilot Al-Athar

When working autonomously or on scheduled runs:
1. Read `AGENTS.md` and pick the first `pending` backlog item only.
2. Do not touch `platform/`.
3. Run `npm run build` before committing.
4. Push to `master` to trigger deploy (Azure backend + Vercel frontend).
5. Mark the backlog item `done` in `AGENTS.md`.
6. Reply in Arabic, concise.

Stack: React 19 + Vite + Tailwind | Express 5 + MongoDB Cosmos | Vercel + Azure.
